      ],
      "id": "a1375b6e-3740-2723-74b2-c72278c5bc95",
      "name": "Note: Diff the Two Systems"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Create Missing in Notion\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Gather Sync Results · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token",
        "width": 280,
